==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Seemer
<hw>Seem"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who seems; one who
carries or assumes an appearance or semblance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Hence shall we see,⟦br⟧
If power change purpose, what our <qex>seemers</qex> be.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seeming</ent>⟦br⟧
